likx (3.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Rebrand from Linux SnipTool to LikX
  * Add Snap Store packaging
  * Add AppImage distribution
  * Full X11 and Wayland support
  * 10 annotation tools (pen, highlighter, arrow, shapes, text, blur, pixelate)
  * OCR text extraction via Tesseract
  * Pin-to-desktop mode
  * Visual effects (shadow, border, rounded corners)
  * Imgur cloud upload

